WWW-CMS version 0.86
=======================

WWW-CMS is an OOP-based, drop-in templating / CMS system for CGI,
mod_perl, or FCGI applications.
Developers are encouraged to submit ideas and/or patches to
shellshark at shellshark dot net.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  strict
  warnings
  POSIX

